42:14.193 --> 42:18.745
When you're the champ,
everybody wants a piece of you.

42:18.783 --> 42:21.079
Everybody’s testing you.

42:21.118 --> 42:26.545
My whole life, I got a problem,
I take care of it with these.

42:26.582 --> 42:29.379
People love a guy who can fight.

42:29.419 --> 42:34.047
Money, pussy, kiss your ass,
put you on TV...

42:34.048 --> 42:36.218
