46:13.359 --> 46:15.029
There is no "you and me."

46:15.068 --> 46:17.114
I'm taking my vacation
right along with the warden.

46:17.154 --> 46:19.074
Well, thank you
for your support.

46:19.114 --> 46:22.120
Oh, come on.
You run the fight program here.

46:22.159 --> 46:24.121
You want this to happen.

46:38.593 --> 46:39.968
Here we go, Monroe.

46:39.969 --> 46:42.600
Free at last, free at last.

46:44.182 --> 46:47.773
-I'm not going to Folsom.
-What can I tell you?

46:47.811 --> 46:51.109
Looks like the warden
went and changed his mind.

46:51.148 --> 46:53.110
You get to stay home with us.

46:59.458 --> 47:02.339
Yeah, Operator,
a collect call to Yank Lewis.

47:02.379 --> 47:05.343
