47:44.840 --> 47:47.721
If it's on the real,
I'll whip on this punk's ass...

47:47.759 --> 47:49.386
and be out of here.

47:49.427 --> 47:52.680
Who's the punk?
Don't tell me Monroe Hutchen.

47:52.681 --> 47:56.397
He fought out of Oakland.
He was undefeated.

47:56.434 --> 48:00.150
He was a real prospect, man.
He's a full load.

48:00.189 --> 48:03.278
