he's been in here for ten years.

48:03.318 --> 48:06.616
I'm just saying it might not be
a walk in the park.

48:06.654 --> 48:08.863
-I don't believe this shit.
-What?

48:08.864 --> 48:10.701
You worried about me
being out of shape.

48:10.702 --> 48:12.035
I've been in here
for four months.

48:12.076 --> 48:13.663
That chump been in here
for ten years.

48:13.703 --> 48:16.541
-You too much, man.
-What? That's concern...

48:16.581 --> 48:18.167
Get the fuck outta here.

48:21.044 --> 48:23.378
Yes, I want you to fight him,

48:23.379 --> 48:28.263
In the cage, no gloves,
bare-fisted, to the finish,

48:28.301 --> 48:31.182
I make a couple of calls,
I put down some money...

48:31.221 --> 48:32.848
There's some people
on the outside...

48:32.889 --> 48:35.725
that know you,
everybody knows him...

48:35.726 --> 48:38.440
we'll get maybe twenty,
thirty-to-one odds,

48:38.479 --> 48:41.610
It's easy to spread around,
maybe two hundred thousand,

48:41.648 --> 48:46.532
