49:08.759 --> 49:10.345
Oh, I don't think so.

49:10.386 --> 49:13.977
I'm putting up all the dough
on a real long shot.

49:14.015 --> 49:15.642
I'm taking all the risk.

49:15.683 --> 49:17.437
What are you worried
about money for?

49:17.438 --> 49:19.564
What are you gonna buy in here?

49:19.603 --> 49:22.359
You in here, too.

49:22.398 --> 49:24.444
Probably gonna die in here.

49:24.484 --> 49:26.697
What the money matter to you?

49:26.737 --> 49:29.158
You're gonna get ten percent.

49:29.198 --> 49:31.369
I know that fighters
usually get...

49:31.408 --> 49:33.787
fifty percent, minimum,
on the outside.

49:33.827 --> 49:37.623
Yeah, but we're not outside.

49:37.624 --> 49:39.501
